These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, white, brown, pink, green
 1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who likes green is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who likes white is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person who likes azure is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the british##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person who likes azure##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Color         | brown | pink    | white | azure  | green |

