.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, time-travel, horror, superhero, epic
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, traveling, writing
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, dutch, egyptian, german, spanish
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile, train
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the spanish##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the australian is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
 5. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the egyptian is on the right of the german##1
 9. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the dutch##1
11. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
13. the person watching superhero movies is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre      | superhero          | horror  | time-travel       | thriller     | epic      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | traveling  | reading   | cooking    |
| Nationality   | dutch        | spanish | australian | german    | egyptian   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | scooter | train      | quad-bike | snowmobile |

