.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
There 5 different types of food: kale, lemon, papaya, plum, zucchini
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, horror, scientific, superhero, time-travel
City: hannover, hamburg, london, new-york, rome
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, taxi, van
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person traveling to hannover is the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating zucchini is the person traveling to london##1
11. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food          | plum        | kale       | papaya | lemon   | zucchini  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific | horror | drama   | superhero |
| City   | new-york         | rome     | hamburg | hannover | london     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

